/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
29/10/2025	navkc1 JIRA 36186 PNL | Vehicle App Swap behaviour with Release Requests - DB Changes / Jade / Form

*/

vars

begin
	// Always initialize the activity first
	self.initialiseActivityWithPassport(_passport, method);

	// Arm our base exception handlers
