Purpose:	To switch a contaienr from one IMV to another, scnario - RTG places container on IMV1 but enters IMV2 ops correct via this trx		

Parameters:			

Return Value:		


Date		Who		Reason
22 April 2010	cnwrd1	Initial creation ccms 1124 par 23362

*/

vars

